headline: Paramount (PSKY) Stock Trades Up, Here Is Why
summary: Shares of multinational media and entertainment corporation Paramount (NASDAQ:PARA) jumped 2.5% in the afternoon session after the company planned to acquire Bari Weiss's media platform, The Free Press, and appoint her as editor-in-chief of CBS News.
